description: This file serves as the entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports core React libraries, stylesheet, and the main App component, then renders the App inside the DOM element with id 'root' using React's createRoot API.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to render React components into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree within the root.
